I had placed an order in advance to secure a cheaper booking slot (scheduled for today evening). However when I checked the app today morning it didn't show me this order as pending. Instead it was listed in the recent orders. Additionally the recent orders aren't sorted in descending order of the date and therefore it is impossible to see the order easily. As a result I thought there isn't any delivery planned for today but the delivery happened. Had I known this before I could have cancelled this order beforehand. Suggestions to improve the app: - the order should be as pending order based on the date AND TIME of the delivery. For e.g. in the case above it should have been listed in pending orders and not in recent orders - the recent orders list should be sorted in descending order of the delivery dates which makes it easy for the user to identify previous orders easily - a system notification should be sent out to the user a day before the scheduled pending orders delivery to remind the user to make last minute changes if any. Currently a text message is sent but a system notification from the app will be more beneficial.

It's about time! Finally a shopping app for Sainsbury's - and it's pretty good. I've placed my first order pretty easily and the interface was great.I have 2 issues so far.1. The app starts to chug after a while of use. Starts smooth and slowly becomes very laggy and slow. A bug that needs squashing there!2. The search isn't as flexible/intuitive as I'd have hoped and on a few occasions I had to be word perfect to find the product I was looking for.It would also be great if you could see a full screen image of the product if you touch the thumbnailOtherwise a great start and look forward to further improvements and optimisations.

All went very well. Searched for items with no problems at all. Very good connection to account showing my previous order as soon as I logged in. From this you can then choose to add the whole previous order to your new orders basket or you can add to basket singularly right there with one click. Checkout was a breeze with the delivery price changing accordingly as per my checkout cost. Overall I am very pleased I downloaded the app and will most definitely be using all the time for future deliveries.
